      <h2>Demystifying platforms</h2>

      <p>GitHub, GitLab, Forgejo, Bitbucket... are <strong>servers</strong> that host <strong><span class="keyword">bare repos</span></strong> and add a <strong>web interface</strong> on top.</p>

